race.comment: FAST KNOCKDOWN (1) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 1.3 lengths away in second (35.15). Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. LAMP POST (7) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 2nd on October 22 over 600m at this track behind JONI BLACK beaten 2.25 lengths (34.85) in a Restricted WIN H. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Expected to be in this for a long way. JONI BLACK (6) was quickly into stride and found the front last start to record an all-the-way win (34.70) at this track in a Restricted WIN H over 600m. Winner at her latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Significant danger. ZARI ELAINE (2) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.
